<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 300 200" width="600" height="400">
  <!-- Simple Vada Pav illustration: bun, vada (patty), chutney -->
  <!-- Bottom bun -->
  <ellipse cx="150" cy="140" rx="120" ry="28" fill="#d99b59" />
  <!-- Vada (fried potato patty) -->
  <g transform="translate(0, -10)">
    <ellipse cx="150" cy="115" rx="80" ry="38" fill="#c76b2b" />
    <ellipse cx="150" cy="105" rx="72" ry="28" fill="#e08a3a" opacity="0.9" />
    <!-- crispy texture -->
    <g fill="#b85b20" opacity="0.7">
      <circle cx="120" cy="100" r="3" />
      <circle cx="135" cy="92" r="2.5" />
      <circle cx="170" cy="98" r="2.7" />
      <circle cx="155" cy="110" r="2.2" />
      <circle cx="185" cy="103" r="2.1" />
    </g>
  </g>
  <!-- Top bun -->
  <path d="M30 110 C30 70, 90 40, 150 40 C210 40, 270 70, 270 110 L270 120 C270 140, 210 170, 150 170 C90 170, 30 140, 30 120 Z"
        fill="#f2c27d" />
  <!-- sesame seeds -->
  <g fill="#fff2d6" opacity="0.9">
    <ellipse cx="70" cy="70" rx="4" ry="2" transform="rotate(-20 70 70)" />
    <ellipse cx="95" cy="60" rx="4" ry="2" transform="rotate(-10 95 60)" />
    <ellipse cx="120" cy="58" rx="4" ry="2" transform="rotate(5 120 58)" />
    <ellipse cx="150" cy="56" rx="4" ry="2" transform="rotate(12 150 56)" />
    <ellipse cx="185" cy="62" rx="4" ry="2" transform="rotate(-8 185 62)" />
    <ellipse cx="210" cy="74" rx="4" ry="2" transform="rotate(6 210 74)" />
  </g>
  <!-- chutney smear -->
  <path d="M95 120 C110 115, 140 125, 160 118 C180 110, 210 120, 220 126"
        stroke="#68b35a" stroke-width="10" stroke-linecap="round" fill="none" opacity="0.95" />
  <!-- small highlights -->
  <ellipse cx="170" cy="40" rx="28" ry="8" fill="#ffdca6" opacity="0.35" />
  <!-- optional label (hidden by default) -->
  <text x="150" y="195" font-family="sans-serif" font-size="12" fill="#666" text-anchor="middle" opacity="0.0">Vada Pav</text>
</svg>
